==制作==
该剧共投资3000万，剧组花费巨资搭建了[[华清池|华清池]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20090515/000163.htm|title=电视剧《李白》8月开机 陈建斌：不会打打杀杀|accessdate=2014-11-29|date=2009-05-15|work=腾讯网|archive-date=2014-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205054611/http://ent.qq.com/a/20090515/000163.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20091030/000264_1.htm|title=《李白》再爆精美剧照 华清池待伊能静大驾光临|date=2009-10-30|accessdate=2014-11-29|work=腾讯网|archive-date=2014-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141205054608/http://ent.qq.com/a/20091030/000264_1.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

